casebody.head_matter:
In Re DEPARTMENT OF COMMERCE, et al., petitioners.
No. 18-557.
Supreme Court of the United States
Nov. 6, 2018.
The respondents are directed to file a response to the petition on or before 5 p.m., Tuesday, November 13, 2018. Petitioners may file a reply brief on or before 2 p.m., Thursday, November 15, 2018. Amicus curiae briefs may be filed on or before 5 p.m., Tuesday, November 13, 2018.
